rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都試過出雪花 耳鳴 出冷汗 次次都嚇到我半死 好怕好怕會再暈 於是係咁search啲有關暈嘅嘢 又話心臟供血有事呀 腦癌呀 甲狀腺乜乜 醫生叫我去再check多次但自從上次抽血暈咗我就好驚再驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一嚟怕又暈 二嚟怕真係有事 我同你都會好怕屋企人有事 有時夜麻麻聽到屋企人去藥櫃攞藥就會驚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係又唔敢同屋企人講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e63759dffd10136ab8e0c2ef9e7a9f7d4dd96c1","tid":791903,"uid":202237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cf44012e11559970db03fedac18ba1dd0bb436f","tid":791903,"uid":201403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"41836337f69ed859849f0014aa8f7ba1e76b5fea","tid":791903,"uid":202237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"我就黎疑病症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為家族遺傳有精神病  阿嫲有焦慮症 大伯抑鬱 老豆躁狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個哥陣有一排壓力太大甩頭發<br />\n日日放左學就去睇醫生問佢我有冇生cancer之類<br />\n真係日日都去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為有得claim<br />\n之後過左一排知道自己壓力太大先咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就冇嘢了<br />\n又有一排黎M前幾日 個心口成日谷住谷住<br />\n我以為自己乳癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日上網睇 以為自己就嚟死<br />\n但係黎完m之後冇谷住 就遺忘左呢件事<br />\n但冇咁簡單<br />\n之後一個暑假我發燒幾日無食嘢<br />\n撘撘下巴士突然間睇唔到嘢<br />\n係有雪花 畫面慢慢變黑<br />\n再聽唔到嘢 耳鳴 出冷汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時以為自己會死<br />\n我第日即刻去睇醫生<br />\n結果遇着個傻閪 不停嚇鳩我 叫我去照MRI <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我梗係俾佢嚇到 即刻book咗<br />\n返到屋企之後不停咁諗 ff自己出事<br />\n再加上我有幽閉恐懼症(同fd去張保仔洞 喺入口縮沙唔敢走入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n一諗到mri要塞自己入個洞 就勁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇到狂喊 瞓唔着 <br />\n老豆就安慰我話家族冇生cancer病史<br />\n又坐係我床邊睇住我瞓覺<br />\n我先瞓得着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過之後成個月都無胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果過左一年<br />\n啱啱睇到人地出cancer報告嘅post（希望佢會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又懷疑自己生cancer 嚇到手都震埋<br />\n最好笑嘅係我會唔敢上網查有關cancer嘅事<br />\n見到差唔多嘅嘢會即刻走 完全唔敢睇<br />\n又唔敢去睇醫生 驚自己真係有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又會不停怕自己屋企人有事<br />\n我就黎神經衰弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"極有共鳴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都試過出雪花 耳鳴 出冷汗 次次都嚇到我半死 好怕好怕會再暈 於是係咁search啲有關暈嘅嘢 又話心臟供血有事呀 腦癌呀 甲狀腺乜乜 醫生叫我去再check多次但自從上次抽血暈咗我就好驚再驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一嚟怕又暈 二嚟怕真係有事 我同你都會好怕屋企人有事 有時夜麻麻聽到屋企人去藥櫃攞藥就會驚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係又唔敢同屋企人講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"啱呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔可以上網查自己有咩病 因為全部都勁嚴重<br />\n一係就大腸癌子宮頸癌 再唔係就腫瘤乜乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好多病都係自己嚇出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就好似我個friend咁<br />\n佢同條仔第一次扑完嘢 結果勁耐冇黎M 佢勁驚自己有咗<br />\n於是我叫佢唔使驚 佢係因為驚得滯所以先冇M<br />\n結果佢心情平復翻之後過幾日就嚟咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以好多野都係自己嚇自己 冇病都會嚇到有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我都係好驚屋企人會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a75157363bdf23512da5036d9ecce3d8130690","tid":791903,"uid":89509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"我曾經以前係朋友圈子入邊係做搞笑嘅人<br />\n但自從有咗焦慮症之後連同朋友傾計都會覺得頭暈心悸<br />\n諗到D好好笑嘅野唔知點解係講唔出口，頭好痛<br />\n最尾決定就摺喺屋企冇晒社交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94908550c0893b6ea1b562fe8233b84eda0be0d","tid":791903,"uid":89968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"以前曾經有ptsd，如果你有發生咩事，唔同醫生講，醫生唔知你以前發生咩事，佢可能因為你冇講某啲野而斷錯症/開錯藥。我以前都on99唔肯講，佢判我做輕度抑鬱，後來講左後佢換左藥，而且佢同我講左啲鼓勵說話，叫我勇敢咁面對以後既人生。"},{"pid":"9ddcab070e09b9cb05f630e7a38c66f3c0832be4","tid":791903,"uid":2806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf44012e11559970db03fedac18ba1dd0bb436f","tid":791903,"uid":201403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"41836337f69ed859849f0014aa8f7ba1e76b5fea","tid":791903,"uid":202237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"我就黎疑病症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為家族遺傳有精神病  阿嫲有焦慮症 大伯抑鬱 老豆躁狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個哥陣有一排壓力太大甩頭發<br />\n日日放左學就去睇醫生問佢我有冇生cancer之類<br />\n真係日日都去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為有得claim<br />\n之後過左一排知道自己壓力太大先咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就冇嘢了<br />\n又有一排黎M前幾日 個心口成日谷住谷住<br />\n我以為自己乳癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日上網睇 以為自己就嚟死<br